# 📊 Online Course Analytics Dashboard

## 🔹 Project Overview

This project analyzes an online learning platform dataset to understand course performance, user behavior, and revenue trends.

---

## 🔧 Tools Used

* Excel (Data Analysis)
* Python (Pandas for Data Processing)
* Power BI (Dashboard)

---

## 📈 Key Features

* Data cleaning and merging using Python
* Feature engineering (Price Band, Duration Band, Rating Band)
* Interactive Power BI dashboard
* KPI metrics and dynamic filters

---

## 📊 Dashboard Insights

* Medium-priced courses generate the highest revenue
* Free courses drive user engagement
* Medium-duration courses perform best

